  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1960330/extras/74444f08a27154f7ff8dea6c6ae37bcb.poster.avif?t=1756402714\" width=620 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1960330/extras/74444f08a27154f7ff8dea6c6ae37bcb.webm?t=1756402714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1960330/extras/74444f08a27154f7ff8dea6c6ae37bcb.mp4?t=1756402714\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to the land of <strong>Alchemia</strong>, where magic and alchemy meet to create fantastical creatures and allow a few individuals to harness powers only dreamt of! In your journeys through this land you'll encounter foes, friends, ancient knowledge and relics from a bygone civilization, and much more!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1960330/extras/124887a8f404d72219602d1d76e67017.avif?t=1756402714\" width=496 height=78 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >35+ different enemies to strategize against and defeat </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >60 unique recipes to discover, with over 10 quintillion possible combinations in each run </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 35+ powerful artifacts to loot and  customize your build </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >20+ detailed events to encounter during journeys </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>...and Much More to Discover!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1960330/extras/6f8b84e97b0de4c477bdc7fc8b111612.poster.avif?t=1756402714\" width=620 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1960330/extras/6f8b84e97b0de4c477bdc7fc8b111612.webm?t=1756402714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1960330/extras/6f8b84e97b0de4c477bdc7fc8b111612.mp4?t=1756402714\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
